title: Skillfeed Photoshop CC Prepare for the Adobe Certified Expert Ex
description:
Skillfeed Photoshop CC Prepare for the Adobe Certified Expert Exam


This course will help you prepare for the Adobe Certified Expert in Photoshop CC Exam. Otherwise known as ACE, this exam is the highest official certification you can get, proving your skills in Photoshop and helping to further your career in the creative industry.

The ACE exam is made up of 10 main topics, which are all covered in great detail. Practice tests are also available for download, to help you to prepare for the real exam and summarize what you have learned
